OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783720149
OL,3,CHospital urgent and emergency care re-
OL,4,Crated as 'requires improvement' by CQC
OL,6,FA hospital in Ashford has been re-
OL,7,Frated as requires improvement by the
OL,8,FCare Quality Commission.
OL,10,FAn inspection of the urgent and
OL,11,Femergency care department at the
OL,12,FWilliam Harvey Hospital found some
OL,13,Fimprovements, including what it
OL,14,Fdescribed as, "caring" staff.
OL,16,FBut inspectors also discovered further
OL,17,Fbreaches of regulations relating to
OL,18,Fsafe care and treatment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783720149
OL,3,CHospital urgent and emergency care re-
OL,4,Crated as 'requires improvement' by CQC
OL,6,FA spokesperson for East Kent Hospitals
OL,7,FNHS Trust - which runs the hospital -
OL,8,Fsaid it accepted the report, adding it
OL,9,Fis "fully committed" to making
OL,10,Fimprovements.
OL,12,FInspectors, who visited the hospital
OL,13,Fin February, said that leaders didn't
OL,14,F"consistently provide sufficient
OL,15,Fcapacity overnight to manage demand".
OL,17,FPatients also failed to receive scans
OL,18,Fin a timely manner, which resulted in
OL,19,Fsome waiting up to 23 hours, the
OL,20,Freport added.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783720149
OL,3,CHospital urgent and emergency care re-
OL,4,Crated as 'requires improvement' by CQC
OL,6,FIt did, however, praise staff for
OL,7,Ftheir effective communication with
OL,8,Fchildren and for providing a safe
OL,9,Fenvironment.
OL,11,FAmanda Williams, CQC deputy director
OL,12,Fof hospitals, secondary and specialist
OL,13,Fcare for Kent, said the review
OL,14,Fcoincided with a critical incident
OL,15,Fbeing declared on the second day of
OL,16,Ftheir visit.
OL,18,FShe said that inspectors noted that
OL,19,Fsome of the challenges experienced by
OL,20,Fthe department were "linked to delays
OL,21,Fin responses from specialist teams".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783720149
OL,3,CHospital urgent and emergency care re-
OL,4,Crated as 'requires improvement' by CQC
OL,6,F"These delays affected the flow of
OL,7,Fpeople through the department,
OL,8,Freducing available capacity and meant
OL,9,Fsome people spent extended periods in
OL,10,Fcorridor areas," she said.
OL,12,FMs Williams added that while the CQC
OL,13,Frecognises that in "times of
OL,14,Fheightened pressure trusts will need
OL,15,Fto make difficult risk-based decisions
OL,16,Fto determine the safest place for
OL,17,Fpeople to be", this does not mean that
OL,18,Fcorridor care can "become normalised".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783720149
OL,3,CHospital urgent and emergency care re-
OL,4,Crated as 'requires improvement' by CQC
OL,6,FShe said: "Leaders at William Harvey
OL,7,FHospital understand the areas where
OL,8,Ffurther improvement is needed and are
OL,9,Ftaking steps to address them.
OL,11,F"CQC will continue to monitor progress
OL,12,Fclosely to ensure people are safe."
OL,14,FDr Des Holden, acting chief executive
OL,15,Ffor East Kent Hospitals, said the
OL,16,Freport was an "accurate reflection of
OL,17,Fthe overcrowding and 'corridor care'".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783720149
OL,3,CHospital urgent and emergency care re-
OL,4,Crated as 'requires improvement' by CQC
OL,6,FHe said: "This is something everyone
OL,7,Fin the Trust has recognised as
OL,8,Funacceptable because we know it has a
OL,9,Fsignificant impact on patients, care,
OL,10,Fsafety, privacy and dignity.
OL,12,F"This year, we have been working as a
OL,13,Fwhole-hospital team, alongside NHS
OL,14,FEngland and with our partner
OL,15,Forganisations, to end corridor care in
OL,16,Four hospitals.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783720149
OL,3,CHospital urgent and emergency care re-
OL,4,Crated as 'requires improvement' by CQC
OL,6,F"Thanks to the hard work of many
OL,7,Fstaff, we now rarely care for a
OL,8,Fpatient in a corridor and we are now
OL,9,Ffocusing our work on eliminating all
OL,10,Fwaits for patients outside a cubicle
OL,11,For bed space anywhere in the hospital."
OL,13,FDr Holden added: "We are fully
OL,14,Fcommitted to continuing to improve our
OL,15,Furgent and emergency care services for
OL,16,Fpatients."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
